OL,6,FHundreds of sub-postmasters wrongly
OL,7,Fconvicted, and in some cases jailed,
OL,8,Fover the Horizon scandal have been
OL,9,Ftold their names will be cleared
OL,10,Fwithin months, but not all will be
OL,11,Fautomatically cleared, ITV News's Amy
OL,12,FLewis reports
