OL,6,FMr Hollinrake said: "The legislation,
OL,7,Fwhich will be brought forward shortly,
OL,8,Fwill quash all convictions which are
OL,9,Fidentified as being in scope.
OL,11,F"That scope will be defined by a set
OL,12,Fof clear and objective criteria which
OL,13,Fwill be set out in the legislation and
OL,14,Fwill not require any element of
OL,15,Fdiscretion or subjective analysis in
OL,16,Forder to be applied."
