OL,6,FThe row began after Mr Staunton gave
OL,7,Fan interview to The Sunday Times in
OL,8,Fwhich he said a senior civil servant
OL,9,Fhad told him to delay compensation
OL,10,Fclaims to sub-postmasters ahead of the
OL,11,Felection.
OL,13,FThis led to a series of rebuttals from
OL,14,FMs Badenoch, Mr Staunton and the
OL,15,Fsenior civil servant involved, Sarah
OL,16,FMunby.
